title: Undergraduate research video competition accepting submissions (Oklahoma State University - Tulsa)
text: ( Source : Oklahoma State University - Tulsa ) Thursday, October 22 , 2015 OSU Research is calling for submissions from students and faculty revealing how undergraduate research impacted their life or career. The deadline for entry is Nov. 1.
